\par }{\ul Horses}{
\par 
\par Bryce: Didn\rquote t you have a team of horses when you broke that land down?
\par 
\par Grandpa: 6 head of horses - Chub and Browny. I can\rquote t remember what I called the Chub one, that dirty one.
